org.dspace.plugin

Interface CommunityHomeProcessor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RecentCommunitySubmissions, SideBarFacetProcessor, TagCloudProcessor

    public interface CommunityHomeProcessor
    Interface that must be implemented by any plugin wanting to be called at the inception of the Community home page (in HandleServlet). Classes that implement the process method and appear in the configuration will be run before the at the start of preparing the community home page has any chance to continue its execution
    Author:
    Richard Jones
